DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL
v.
BALDWIN 2018-1087 Supreme Court of Ohio. September 11, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On certified order of the Supreme Court of Illinois, No. 2017PR00110. Scott Michael Baldwin, Attorney Registration No. 0062522, last known address in Metamora, Illinois, suspended from the practice of law in Ohio for two years.
